=head1 NAME

_CONCAT_FTS_SCANS_ - Find and concatenate scans of the moving mirror

=head1 SYNOPSIS

 _CONCAT_FTS_SCANS_

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive identifies files which comprise scans of the FTS
moving mirror, and concatenates them.

=head1 ARGUMENTS

None.

=head1 EXTERNAL TASKS

None.

=head1 OUTPUT DATA

None

=head1 OUTPUT FILES

None.

=head1 NOTES

None.

